    "@value" : "2026-04-12"
  } ],
  "http://purl.org/dc/terms/description" : [ {
    "@value" : "An ontology modelling the European catalogue of high-risk medical devices and in-vitro diagnostics under MDR (EU 2017/745) and IVDR (EU 2017/746) regulations."
